REST (Principles)

- Resources (CRUD)
  - name : plural. students, books

- URL - HTTP Methods
  - Create a new book : /api/v1/books : POST
  - Update a book : /api/v1/books/<resource-id> : PUT
  - Get a book : /api/v1/books/<resource-id> : GET
  - Get all books : /api/v1/books : GET
  - Delete a book : /api/v1/books/<resource-id> : DELETE
  - Filter the books : /api/v1/books?title=Book1 : GET

- Response codes
  - Success
    - POST : 201
    - GET : 200
    - PUT : 200
    - DELETE : 204 or 200
  - Error
    - Client initiated error : 4xx
    - Server initiated error : 5xx

- Request/Response data formats
  - JSON/XML
